text: Phyllanthus raiateaensis is a species of tree in the family Phyllanthaceae. It is endemic to the Te Mehani Plateau on the island of Raiatea in the Society Islands of French Polynesia.Florence, J. (1997) Flore de la Polynésie française, vol. 1.
